{
  "stem": "22469.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And his boss, he was a Polish officer what was Jewish.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they-- the German took him as prisoner of war.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my brother was the manager after the German give him another boss.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They took away the pharmacy from the Jews.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "David.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 120,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My younger brother, the same.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 120,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He learned because he want to go to Palestine.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 120,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Locksmith.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 120,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But '38, he wasn't finished with his-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] with his learning.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 120,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So he went to Russia because he don't like-- he didn't like to be with German.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 120,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In Russia, the people told me, came with the return from Russia, he told me that they met him.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 120,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he voluntary went to Polish army in Russia to fight the German.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 120,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "In '41, when the German attacked Russia, he-- the Polish army went against Germany, And he fell.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 120,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They killed him.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 121,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My parents, this was not-- the men, they were forced to clean the street, and ordinary work to do without salary.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 121,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we're struggling.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 121,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Just we struggling.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 122,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Cracow.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 123,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 123,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Before-- until '40, we have been nowhere in Cracow.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 124,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes. '40, we went to the village.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 124,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the peasant around, they start to ask what I'm doing.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 124,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I said, I'm painting.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 124,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And suddenly it was occurred to me, because I was very busy every day, wanted to-- from Cracow a painter, it was something special for the peasant.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 124,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So-- but the salary, I didn't take money.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 124,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Just food.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 124,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And so we--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 125,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 125,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was living with my parents.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 126,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Zielonki.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 127,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This is like 10 miles from Cracow.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 128,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We'd been from '40 until '41.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 128,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] That is what-- June.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 129,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Over one year.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 130,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "With my parents.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 131,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In a flat.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 131,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "One room.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 131,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In one room.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 132,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My brother was in Cracow, in ghetto.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
